X,Y
[0,1]
A=\min (X,Y), B=\max (X,Y)
C=\max (A, 1-B, B-A)
f_C(a)
C
F_C(a)
C
 F_C(a) = P(C\le a)=P(A\le a, 1-B\le a, B-A\le a).
F_C(a)=\left\{\begin{array}{ll} (3a-1)^2 & \frac{1}{3}\le a\le \frac{1}{2}\\ 1-3(1-a)^2 & \frac{1}{2}\le a\le 1\end{array}\right.
f_C(a)=\left\{\begin{array}{ll} 6(3a-1) & \frac{1}{3}\le a\le \frac{1}{2}\\ 6(1-a) & \frac{1}{2}\le a\le 1\end{array}\right.
\int_{1/3} ^{1/2}6a(3a-1) da+\int_{1/2} ^{1}6a(1-a) da= \frac{11}{18}.
n>3
